file: bmptk/hardware/README

Bare Metal Programming Tool Kit hardware interfacing directory

This directory contains chip-independent hardware interfaces: pins,
ports, I2c, SPI, etc.

files
   demos.h            : demo's like blink, beep, kitt
   ic2.h              : I2C interafce
	Makefile           : dummy makefile
   pins.h             : pin abstractions
   ports.h            : port abstractions
   README             : this file
   spi.h              : SPI intertface

